<span id="fn_182"></span>[86:4](sbe20024.htm#fr_187.md) Patta-ka*nd*olikâ
ti mahâ-mukha-ku*nd*a-sa*nth*ânâ bhandakukkha*li*knâ vu*kk*ati (B.).
Ka*nd*ola is a wicker-work basket; see Böhtlingk-Roth, sub voce.

<span id="fn_183"></span>[86:5](sbe20024.htm#fr_188.md) See H.O.'s note on
the reading here; and compare the table of contents to this chapter (at
p. 143), where the reading a*m*sabaddha*m* confirms the suggested
